FLOW MATCHING FOR GENERATIVE MODELING

用于生成建模的流匹配

Yaron Lipman 1,2 Ricky T. Q. Chen 1 Heli Ben-Hamu 2 Maximilian Nickel 1 Matt Le 1

Yaron Lipman 1,2 Ricky T. Q. Chen 1 Heli Ben-Hamu 2 Maximilian Nickel 1 Matt Le 1

1 Meta AI (FAIR) 2 Weizmann Institute of Science

1 Meta AI (FAIR) 2 魏茨曼科学研究院

Abstract

摘要

We introduce a new paradigm for generative modeling built on Continuous Normalizing Flows (CNFs), allowing us to train CNFs at unprecedented scale. Specifically, we present the notion of Flow Matching (FM), a simulation-free approach for training CNFs based on regressing vector fields of fixed conditional probability paths. Flow Matching is compatible with a general family of Gaussian probability paths for transforming between noise and data samples-which subsumes existing diffusion paths as specific instances. Interestingly, we find that employing FM with diffusion paths results in a more robust and stable alternative for training diffusion models. Furthermore, Flow Matching opens the door to training CNFs with other, non-diffusion probability paths. An instance of particular interest is using Optimal Transport (OT) displacement interpolation to define the conditional probability paths. These paths are more efficient than diffusion paths, provide faster training and sampling, and result in better generalization. Training CNFs using Flow Matching on ImageNet leads to consistently better performance than alternative diffusion-based methods in terms of both likelihood and sample quality, and allows fast and reliable sample generation using off-the-shelf numerical ODE solvers.

我们提出了一种基于连续归一化流（Continuous Normalizing Flows, CNFs）的生成建模新范式，使得我们能够以前所未有的规模训练CNFs。具体而言，我们引入了流匹配（Flow Matching, FM）的概念，这是一种基于回归固定条件概率路径的向量场的无模拟训练CNFs的方法。流匹配兼容一类通用的高斯概率路径，用于在噪声和数据样本之间转换——该路径包含现有的扩散路径作为特例。有趣的是，我们发现将流匹配应用于扩散路径时，能够为扩散模型训练提供更稳健和稳定的替代方案。此外，流匹配为使用其他非扩散概率路径训练CNFs打开了大门。其中一个特别感兴趣的实例是使用最优传输（Optimal Transport, OT）位移插值来定义条件概率路径。这些路径比扩散路径更高效，训练和采样更快，并且具有更好的泛化能力。在ImageNet上使用流匹配训练CNFs，在似然和样本质量方面均持续优于基于扩散的替代方法，并且允许使用现成的数值常微分方程（ODE）求解器快速且可靠地生成样本。

1 INTRODUCTION

1 引言

Deep generative models are a class of deep learning algorithms aimed at estimating and sampling from an unknown data distribution. The recent influx of amazing advances in generative modeling, e.g., for image generation Ramesh et al. (2022); Rombach et al. (2022), is mostly facilitated by the scalable and relatively stable training of diffusion-based models Ho et al. (2020); Song et al. (2020b). However, the restriction to simple diffusion processes leads to a rather confined space of sampling probability paths, resulting in very long training times and the need to adopt specialized methods (e.g., Song et al. (2020a); Zhang & Chen (2022)) for efficient sampling.

深度生成模型是一类旨在估计和采样未知数据分布的深度学习算法。近年来生成建模的惊人进展，例如图像生成（Ramesh et al. (2022); Rombach et al. (2022)），主要得益于基于扩散模型的可扩展且相对稳定的训练（Ho et al. (2020); Song et al. (2020b)）。然而，受限于简单的扩散过程，采样概率路径空间较为狭窄，导致训练时间非常长，并且需要采用专门的方法（例如Song et al. (2020a); Zhang & Chen (2022)）以实现高效采样。

In this work we consider the general and deterministic framework of Continuous Normalizing Flows (CNFs; Chen et al. (2018)). CNFs are capable of modeling arbitrary probability path and are in particular known to encompass the probability paths modeled by diffusion processes (Song et al., 2021). However, aside from diffusion that can be trained efficiently via, e.g., denoising score matching (Vincent, 2011), no scalable CNF training algorithms are known. Indeed, maximum likelihood training (e.g., Grathwohl et al. (2018)) require expensive numerical ODE simulations, while existing simulation-free methods either involve intractable integrals (Rozen et al., 2021) or biased gradients (Ben-Hamu et al., 2022).

本文考虑连续归一化流（Continuous Normalizing Flows, CNFs; Chen et al. (2018)）的通用确定性框架。CNFs能够建模任意概率路径，且特别已知包含由扩散过程建模的概率路径（Song et al., 2021）。然而，除扩散外，目前尚无可扩展的CNF训练算法，扩散可通过去噪分数匹配（denoising score matching）（Vincent, 2011）高效训练。实际上，最大似然训练（如Grathwohl et al. (2018)）需要昂贵的数值常微分方程模拟，而现有的无模拟方法要么涉及难以处理的积分（Rozen et al., 2021），要么存在偏差梯度（Ben-Hamu et al., 2022）。

Figure 1: Unconditional ImageNet-128 samples of a CNF trained using Flow Matching with Optimal Transport probability paths.

图1：使用流匹配和最优传输概率路径训练的CNF在ImageNet-128上的无条件样本。

The goal of this work is to propose Flow Matching (FM), an efficient simulation-free approach to training CNF models, allowing the adoption of general probability paths to supervise CNF training. Importantly, FM breaks the barriers for scalable CNF training beyond diffusion, and sidesteps the need to reason about diffusion processes to directly work with probability paths. In particular, we propose the Flow Matching objective (Section 3), a simple and intuitive training objective to regress onto a target vector field that generates a desired probability path. We first show that we can construct such target vector fields through per-example (i.e., conditional) formulations. Then, inspired by denoising score matching, we show that a per-example training objective, termed Conditional Flow Matching (CFM), provides equivalent gradients and does not require explicit knowledge of the intractable target vector field. Furthermore, we discuss a general family of per-example probability paths (Section 4) that can be used for Flow Matching, which subsumes existing diffusion paths as special instances. Even on diffusion paths, we find that using FM provides more robust and stable training, and achieves superior performance compared to score matching. Furthermore, this family of probability paths also includes a particularly interesting case: the vector field that corresponds to an Optimal Transport (OT) displacement interpolant (McCann, 1997). We find that conditional OT paths are simpler than diffusion paths, forming straight line trajectories whereas diffusion paths result in curved paths. These properties seem to empirically translate to faster training, faster generation, and better performance.

本工作的目标是提出流匹配（Flow Matching, FM），一种高效的无模拟CNF训练方法，允许采用通用概率路径监督CNF训练。重要的是，FM打破了扩散之外可扩展CNF训练的壁垒，避免了必须基于扩散过程推理，直接使用概率路径。具体而言，我们提出了流匹配目标（第3节），这是一种简单直观的训练目标，用于回归生成期望概率路径的目标向量场。我们首先展示了如何通过逐样本（即条件）形式构造此类目标向量场。随后，受去噪分数匹配启发，我们提出了逐样本训练目标，称为条件流匹配（Conditional Flow Matching, CFM），其梯度等价且无需显式知道难以求解的目标向量场。此外，我们讨论了一类可用于流匹配的逐样本概率路径（第4节），该类包含现有扩散路径作为特例。即使在扩散路径上，我们发现使用FM能提供更稳健稳定的训练，并且性能优于分数匹配。此外，该概率路径族还包括一个特别有趣的情况：对应于最优传输（Optimal Transport, OT）位移插值的向量场（McCann, 1997）。我们发现条件OT路径比扩散路径更简单，形成直线路径，而扩散路径则是曲线路径。这些性质在经验上转化为更快的训练、更快的生成和更好的性能。

We empirically validate Flow Matching and the construction via Optimal Transport paths on Im-ageNet, a large and highly diverse image dataset. We find that we can easily train models to achieve favorable performance in both likelihood estimation and sample quality amongst competing diffusion-based methods. Furthermore, we find that our models produce better trade-offs between computational cost and sample quality compared to prior methods. Figure 1 depicts selected unconditional ImageNet 128×128 samples from our model.

我们在ImageNet这一大型且高度多样化的图像数据集上，实证验证了流匹配（Flow Matching）及通过最优传输路径构建的方法。我们发现，可以轻松训练模型，在似然估计和样本质量方面均能在竞争的基于扩散的方法中取得良好表现。此外，我们发现与以往方法相比，我们的模型在计算成本与样本质量之间实现了更优的权衡。图1展示了我们模型生成的部分无条件ImageNet128×128样本。

2 PRELIMINARIES: CONTINUOUS NORMALIZING FLOWS

2 预备知识：连续归一化流

Let Rd denote the data space with data points x=(x1,…,xd)∈Rd . Two important objects we use in this paper are: the probability density path p:[0,1]×Rd→R>0 ,which is a time dependent 1 probability density function,i.e., ∫pt(x)dx=1 ,and a time-dependent vector field, v:[0,1]×Rd→Rd . A vector field vt can be used to construct a time-dependent diffeomorphic map,called a flow, ϕ:[0,1]×Rd→Rd ,defined via the ordinary differential equation (ODE):

设Rd表示数据空间，数据点为x=(x1,…,xd)∈Rd。本文使用的两个重要对象是：概率密度路径p:[0,1]×Rd→R>0，即时间依赖的1概率密度函数，即∫pt(x)dx=1，以及时间依赖的向量场v:[0,1]×Rd→Rd。向量场vt可用于构造时间依赖的微分同胚映射，称为流ϕ:[0,1]×Rd→Rd，其定义通过常微分方程（ODE）：

(1)ddtϕt(x)=vt(ϕt(x))

(2)ϕ0(x)=x

Previously,Chen et al. (2018) suggested modeling the vector field vt with a neural network, vt(x;θ) , where θ∈Rp are its learnable parameters,which in turn leads to a deep parametric model of the flow ϕt ,called a Continuous Normalizing Flow (CNF). A CNF is used to reshape a simple prior density p0 (e.g.,pure noise) to a more complicated one, p1 ,via the push-forward equation

此前，Chen等人（2018）提出用神经网络vt(x;θ)对向量场vt建模，其中θ∈Rp为其可学习参数，从而得到流ϕt的深度参数模型，称为连续归一化流（Continuous Normalizing Flow，CNF）。CNF用于将简单的先验密度p0（例如纯噪声）通过推前方程变换为更复杂的密度p1。

(3)pt=[ϕt]∗p0

where the push-forward (or change of variables) operator ∗ is defined by

其中推前算子（或变量变换算子）∗定义为

(4)[ϕt]∗p0(x)=p0(ϕt−1(x))det[∂ϕt−1∂x(x)].

A vector field vt is said to generate a probability density path pt if its flow ϕt satisfies equation 3 . One practical way to test if a vector field generates a probability path is using the continuity equation, which is a key component in our proofs, see Appendix B. We recap more information on CNFs, in particular how to compute the probability p1(x) at an arbitrary point x∈Rd in Appendix C.

若向量场vt的流ϕt满足方程3，则称其生成概率密度路径pt。检验向量场是否生成概率路径的一个实用方法是使用连续性方程，该方程是我们证明的关键组成部分，详见附录B。我们在附录C中回顾了更多关于CNF的信息，特别是如何计算任意点x∈Rd处的概率p1(x)。

3 FLOW MATCHING

3 流匹配

Let x1 denote a random variable distributed according to some unknown data distribution q(x1) . We assume we only have access to data samples from q(x1) but have no access to the density function itself. Furthermore,we let pt be a probability path such that p0=p is a simple distribution,e.g.,the standard normal distribution p(x)=N(x∣0,I) ,and let p1 be approximately equal in distribution to q . We will later discuss how to construct such a path. The Flow Matching objective is then designed to match this target probability path,which will allow us to flow from p0 to p1 .

设x1为服从某未知数据分布q(x1)的随机变量。我们假设仅能获得来自q(x1)的数据样本，但无法直接访问其密度函数。此外，设pt为概率路径，使得p0=p为简单分布，例如标准正态分布p(x)=N(x∣0,I)，且p1在分布上近似等于q。稍后我们将讨论如何构造这样的路径。流匹配目标即设计为匹配该目标概率路径，从而实现从p0到p1的流动。

1 We use subscript to denote the time parameter,e.g., pt(x) .

1 我们用下标表示时间参数，例如pt(x)。

Given a target probability density path pt(x) and a corresponding vector field ut(x) ,which generates pt(x) ,we define the Flow Matching (FM) objective as

给定目标概率密度路径pt(x)及其对应的生成pt(x)的向量场ut(x)，我们定义流匹配（Flow Matching，FM）目标为

(5)LFM(θ)=Et,pt(x)‖vt(x)−ut(x)‖2,

where θ denotes the learnable parameters of the CNF vector field vt (as defined in Section 2), t∼ U[0,1] (uniform distribution),and x∼pt(x) . Simply put,the FM loss regresses the vector field ut with a neural network vt . Upon reaching zero loss,the learned CNF model will generate pt(x) .

其中θ表示可学习的连续正规流（Continuous Normalizing Flow，CNF）向量场vt的参数（如第2节所定义），t∼ U[0,1]（均匀分布），以及x∼pt(x)。简而言之，FM损失通过神经网络vt回归向量场ut。当损失达到零时，学习到的CNF模型将生成pt(x)。

Flow Matching is a simple and attractive objective, but naïvely on its own, it is intractable to use in practice since we have no prior knowledge for what an appropriate pt and ut are. There are many choices of probability paths that can satisfy p1(x)≈q(x) ,and more importantly,we generally don’t have access to a closed form ut that generates the desired pt . In this section,we show that we can construct both pt and ut using probability paths and vector fields that are only defined per sample,and an appropriate method of aggregation provides the desired pt and ut . Furthermore,this construction allows us to create a much more tractable objective for Flow Matching.

流匹配是一个简单且有吸引力的目标，但单独使用时，因缺乏对合适的pt和ut的先验知识，实际上难以应用。存在许多满足p1(x)≈q(x)的概率路径选择，更重要的是，我们通常无法获得生成期望pt的闭式向量场ut。本节展示了如何利用仅对样本定义的概率路径和向量场构造pt和ut，并通过适当的聚合方法得到期望的pt和ut。此外，该构造使得流匹配目标更加易于处理。

3.1 CONSTRUCTING pt,ut FROM CONDITIONAL PROBABILITY PATHS AND VECTOR FIELDS

3.1 从条件概率路径和向量场构造pt,ut

A simple way to construct a target probability path is via a mixture of simpler probability paths: Given a particular data sample x1 we denote by pt(x∣x1) a conditional probability path such that it satisfies p0(x∣x1)=p(x) at time t=0 ,and we design p1(x∣x1) at t=1 to be a distribution concentrated around x=x1 ,e.g., p1(x∣x1)=N(x∣x1,σ2I) ,a normal distribution with x1 mean and a sufficiently small standard deviation σ>0 . Marginalizing the conditional probability paths over q(x1) give rise to the marginal probability path

构造目标概率路径的一种简单方法是通过更简单概率路径的混合：给定特定数据样本x1，我们用pt(x∣x1)表示满足在时间t=0满足p0(x∣x1)=p(x)的条件概率路径，并设计在t=1时的p1(x∣x1)为集中于x=x1附近的分布，例如均值为x1、标准差足够小的正态分布p1(x∣x1)=N(x∣x1,σ2I)。对q(x1)上的条件概率路径进行边缘化，得到边缘概率路径

(6)pt(x)=∫pt(x∣x1)q(x1)dx1,

where in particular at time t=1 ,the marginal probability p1 is a mixture distribution that closely approximates the data distribution q ,

特别地，在时间t=1，边缘概率p1是一个混合分布，能够很好地近似数据分布q，

(7)p1(x)=∫p1(x∣x1)q(x1)dx1≈q(x).

Interestingly, we can also define a marginal vector field, by "marginalizing" over the conditional vector fields in the following sense (we assume pt(x)>0 for all t and x ):

有趣的是，我们也可以定义边缘向量场，通过以下方式对条件向量场进行“边缘化”（假设对所有t和x均成立pt(x)>0）：

(8)ut(x)=∫ut(x∣x1)pt(x∣x1)q(x1)pt(x)dx1,

where ut(⋅∣x1):Rd→Rd is a conditional vector field that generates pt(⋅∣x1) . It may not seem apparent, but this way of aggregating the conditional vector fields actually results in the correct vector field for modeling the marginal probability path.

其中ut(⋅∣x1):Rd→Rd是生成pt(⋅∣x1)的条件向量场。虽然表面上不明显，但这种聚合条件向量场的方法实际上得到了用于建模边缘概率路径的正确向量场。

Our first key observation is this:

我们的第一个关键观察是：

The marginal vector field (equation 8) generates the marginal probability path (equation 6).

边缘向量场（方程8）生成边缘概率路径（方程6）。

This provides a surprising connection between the conditional VFs (those that generate conditional probability paths) and the marginal VF (those that generate the marginal probability path). This connection allows us to break down the unknown and intractable marginal VF into simpler conditional VFs, which are much simpler to define as these only depend on a single data sample. We formalize this in the following theorem.

这提供了条件向量场（生成条件概率路径的向量场）与边缘向量场（生成边缘概率路径的向量场）之间的一个令人惊讶的联系。该联系使我们能够将未知且难以处理的边缘向量场分解为更简单的条件向量场，这些条件向量场仅依赖于单个数据样本，因此定义起来更为简单。我们在以下定理中对此进行了形式化描述。

Theorem 1. Given vector fields ut(x∣x1) that generate conditional probability paths pt(x∣x1) ,for any distribution q(x1) ,the marginal vector field ut in equation 8 generates the marginal probability path pt in equation 6,i.e., ut and pt satisfy the continuity equation (equation 26).

定理1. 给定生成条件概率路径的向量场ut(x∣x1)，对于任意分布q(x1)，方程8中的边缘向量场ut生成方程6中的边缘概率路径pt，即ut和pt满足连续性方程（方程26）。

The full proofs for our theorems are all provided in Appendix A. Theorem 1 can also be derived from the Diffusion Mixture Representation Theorem in Peluchetti (2021) that provides a formula for the marginal drift and diffusion coefficients in diffusion SDEs.

我们所有定理的完整证明均见附录A。定理1也可以从Peluchetti (2021)中的扩散混合表示定理（Diffusion Mixture Representation Theorem）推导，该定理提供了扩散随机微分方程中边缘漂移和扩散系数的公式。

3.2 CONDITIONAL FLOW MATCHING

3.2 条件流匹配

Unfortunately, due to the intractable integrals in the definitions of the marginal probability path and VF (equations 6 and 8),it is still intractable to compute ut ,and consequently,intractable to naïvely compute an unbiased estimator of the original Flow Matching objective. Instead, we propose a simpler objective, which surprisingly will result in the same optima as the original objective. Specifically, we consider the Conditional Flow Matching (CFM) objective,

不幸的是，由于边缘概率路径和向量场定义中的积分不可解（方程6和8），计算ut仍然是不可行的，因此也无法简单地计算原始流匹配目标的无偏估计。相反，我们提出了一个更简单的目标，令人惊讶的是，该目标将导致与原始目标相同的最优解。具体而言，我们考虑条件流匹配（Conditional Flow Matching，CFM）目标，

(9)LCFM(θ)=Et,q(x1),pt(x∣x1)‖vt(x)−ut(x∣x1)‖2,

where t∼U[0,1],x1∼q(x1) ,and now x∼pt(x∣x1) . Unlike the FM objective,the CFM objective allows us to easily sample unbiased estimates as long as we can efficiently sample from pt(x∣x1) and compute ut(x∣x1) ,both of which can be easily done as they are defined on a per-sample basis. Our second key observation is therefore:

其中t∼U[0,1],x1∼q(x1)，现在为x∼pt(x∣x1)。与流匹配（FM）目标不同，CFM目标允许我们只要能有效从pt(x∣x1)采样并计算ut(x∣x1)，就能轻松采样无偏估计，这两者都很容易实现，因为它们是基于单个样本定义的。因此，我们的第二个关键观察是：

The FM (equation 5) and CFM (equation 9) objectives have identical gradients w.r.t. θ.

流匹配（方程5）和条件流匹配（方程9）目标关于θ的梯度是相同的。

That is, optimizing the CFM objective is equivalent (in expectation) to optimizing the FM objective. Consequently,this allows us to train a CNF to generate the marginal probability path pt —which in particular,approximates the unknown data distribution q at t=1 - without ever needing access to either the marginal probability path or the marginal vector field. We simply need to design suitable conditional probability paths and vector fields. We formalize this property in the following theorem.

也就是说，优化CFM目标在期望意义上等价于优化FM目标。因此，这使我们能够训练条件神经流（CNF）生成边缘概率路径pt——特别是，在t=1时逼近未知的数据分布q——而无需访问边缘概率路径或边缘向量场。我们只需设计合适的条件概率路径和向量场。我们在以下定理中形式化了这一性质。

Theorem 2. Assuming that pt(x)>0 for all x∈Rd and t∈[0,1] ,then,up to a constant independent of θ,LCFM and LFM are equal. Hence, ∇θLFM(θ)=∇θLCFM(θ) .

定理2. 假设对于所有x∈Rd和t∈[0,1]，pt(x)>0，则在与θ,LCFM无关的常数项下，LFM相等。因此，∇θLFM(θ)=∇θLCFM(θ)。

4 CONDITIONAL PROBABILITY PATHS AND VECTOR FIELDS

4 条件概率路径与向量场

The Conditional Flow Matching objective works with any choice of conditional probability path and conditional vector fields. In this section,we discuss the construction of pt(x∣x1) and ut(x∣x1) for a general family of Gaussian conditional probability paths. Namely, we consider conditional probability paths of the form

条件流匹配目标适用于任意选择的条件概率路径和条件向量场。本节中，我们讨论一类通用的高斯条件概率路径的构造，即考虑形式为

(10)pt(x∣x1)=N(x∣μt(x1),σt(x1)2I),

where μ:[0,1]×Rd→Rd is the time-dependent mean of the Gaussian distribution,while σ : [0,1]×R→R>0 describes a time-dependent scalar standard deviation (std). We set μ0(x1)=0 and σ0(x1)=1 ,so that all conditional probability paths converge to the same standard Gaussian noise distribution at t=0,p(x)=N(x∣0,I) . We then set μ1(x1)=x1 and σ1(x1)=σmin ,which is set sufficiently small so that p1(x∣x1) is a concentrated Gaussian distribution centered at x1 .

其中 μ:[0,1]×Rd→Rd 是高斯分布的时间依赖均值，σ : [0,1]×R→R>0 描述时间依赖的标量标准差（std）。我们设定 μ0(x1)=0 和 σ0(x1)=1 ，使得所有条件概率路径在 t=0,p(x)=N(x∣0,I) 时刻收敛到相同的标准高斯噪声分布。然后我们设定 μ1(x1)=x1 和 σ1(x1)=σmin ，其值足够小，使得 p1(x∣x1) 是以 x1 为中心的集中高斯分布。

There is an infinite number of vector fields that generate any particular probability path (e.g., by adding a divergence free component to the continuity equation, see equation 26 ), but the vast majority of these is due to the presence of components that leave the underlying distribution invariant-for instance, rotational components when the distribution is rotation-invariant-leading to unnecessary extra compute. We decide to use the simplest vector field corresponding to a canonical transformation for Gaussian distributions. Specifically,consider the flow (conditioned on x1 )

存在无限多个向量场可以生成任意特定的概率路径（例如，通过在连续性方程中添加无散度分量，见方程26），但绝大多数是由于存在保持底层分布不变的分量——例如，当分布具有旋转不变性时的旋转分量——导致不必要的额外计算。我们决定使用对应于高斯分布的典型变换的最简单向量场。具体地，考虑条件于 x1 的流动

(11)ψt(x)=σt(x1)x+μt(x1).

When x is distributed as a standard Gaussian, ψt(x) is the affine transformation that maps to a normally-distributed random variable with mean μt(x1) and std σt(x1) . That is to say,according to equation 4, ψt pushes the noise distribution p0(x∣x1)=p(x) to pt(x∣x1) ,i.e.,

当 x 服从标准高斯分布时，ψt(x) 是将其映射为均值为 μt(x1)、标准差为 σt(x1) 的正态分布随机变量的仿射变换。也就是说，根据方程4，ψt 将噪声分布 p0(x∣x1)=p(x) 推送到 pt(x∣x1)，即

(12)[ψt]∗p(x)=pt(x∣x1).

This flow then provides a vector field that generates the conditional probability path:

该流动随后提供了生成条件概率路径的向量场：

(13)ddtψt(x)=ut(ψt(x)∣x1).

Reparameterizing pt(x∣x1) in terms of just x0 and plugging equation 13 in the CFM loss we get

用仅由 x0 表示的 pt(x∣x1) 重新参数化，并将方程13代入CFM损失，我们得到

(14)LCFM(θ)=Et,q(x1),p(x0)‖vt(ψt(x0))−ddtψt(x0)‖2.

Since ψt is a simple (invertible) affine map we can use equation 13 to solve for ut in a closed form. Let f′ denote the derivative with respect to time,i.e., f′=ddtf ,for a time-dependent function f .

由于 ψt 是一个简单的（可逆）仿射映射，我们可以用方程13闭式求解 ut。令 f′ 表示对时间的导数，即 f′=ddtf，对于时间依赖函数 f。

Theorem 3. Let pt(x∣x1) be a Gaussian probability path as in equation 10,and ψt its corresponding flow map as in equation 11. Then,the unique vector field that defines ψt has the form:

定理3. 设 pt(x∣x1) 是如方程10所示的高斯概率路径，ψt 是其对应的流映射，如方程11所示。则定义 ψt 的唯一向量场具有以下形式：

(15)ut(x∣x1)=σt′(x1)σt(x1)(x−μt(x1))+μt′(x1).

Consequently, ut(x∣x1) generates the Gaussian path pt(x∣x1) .

因此，ut(x∣x1) 生成了高斯路径 pt(x∣x1)。

4.1 SPECIAL INSTANCES OF GAUSSIAN CONDITIONAL PROBABILITY PATHS

4.1 高斯条件概率路径的特殊实例

Our formulation is fully general for arbitrary functions μt(x1) and σt(x1) ,and we can set them to any differentiable function satisfying the desired boundary conditions. We first discuss the special cases that recover probability paths corresponding to previously-used diffusion processes. Since we directly work with probability paths, we can simply depart from reasoning about diffusion processes altogether. Therefore, in the second example below, we directly formulate a probability path based on the Wasserstein-2 optimal transport solution as an interesting instance.

我们的公式对于任意函数μt(x1)和σt(x1)完全通用，且我们可以将它们设置为满足所需边界条件的任意可微函数。我们首先讨论恢复先前使用的扩散过程对应概率路径的特殊情况。由于我们直接处理概率路径，因此可以完全摒弃对扩散过程的推理。因此，在下面的第二个例子中，我们直接基于Wasserstein-2最优传输解构造了一个概率路径，作为一个有趣的实例。

Example I: Diffusion conditional VFs. Diffusion models start with data points and gradually add noise until it approximates pure noise. These can be formulated as stochastic processes, which have strict requirements in order to obtain closed form representation at arbitrary times t ,resulting in Gaussian conditional probability paths pt(x∣x1) with specific choices of mean μt(x1) and std σt(x1) (Sohl-Dickstein et al.,2015; Ho et al.,2020; Song et al.,2020b). For example,the reversed (noise → data) Variance Exploding (VE) path has the form

例子一：扩散条件向量场。扩散模型从数据点开始，逐渐添加噪声，直到近似纯噪声。这些可以被表述为随机过程，为了在任意时间t获得闭式表示，这些过程有严格要求，导致高斯条件概率路径pt(x∣x1)，其均值μt(x1)和标准差σt(x1)具有特定选择（Sohl-Dickstein等，2015；Ho等，2020；Song等，2020b）。例如，反向（噪声→数据）方差爆炸（VE）路径的形式为

(16)pt(x)=N(x∣x1,σ1−t2I),

where σt is an increasing function, σ0=0 ,and σ1≫1 . Next,equation 16 provides the choices of μt(x1)=x1 and σt(x1)=σ1−t . Plugging these into equation 15 of Theorem 3 we get

其中σt是递增函数，σ0=0，和σ1≫1。接下来，方程16给出了μt(x1)=x1和σt(x1)=σ1−t的选择。将这些代入定理3的方程15，我们得到

(17)ut(x∣x1)=−σ1−t′σ1−t(x−x1).

The reversed (noise → data) Variance Preserving (VP) diffusion path has the form

反向（噪声→数据）方差保持（VP）扩散路径的形式为

(18)pt(x∣x1)=N(x∣α1−tx1,(1−α1−t2)I),whereαt=e−12T(t),T(t)=∫0tβ(s)ds,

and β is the noise scale function. Equation 18 provides the choices of μt(x1)=α1−tx1 and σt(x1)=1−α1−t2 . Plugging these into equation 15 of Theorem 3 we get

且β是噪声尺度函数。方程18给出了μt(x1)=α1−tx1和σt(x1)=1−α1−t2的选择。将这些代入定理3的方程15，我们得到

(19)ut(x∣x1)=α1−t′1−α1−t2(α1−tx−x1)=−T′(1−t)2[e−T(1−t)x−e−12T(1−t)x11−e−T(1−t)].

Our construction of the conditional VF ut(x∣x1) does in fact coincide with the vector field previously used in the deterministic probability flow (Song et al. (2020b), equation 13) when restricted to these conditional diffusion processes; see details in Appendix D. Nevertheless, combining the diffusion conditional VF with the Flow Matching objective offers an attractive training alternative-which we find to be more stable and robust in our experiments-to existing score matching approaches.

我们构造的条件向量场ut(x∣x1)实际上与限制在这些条件扩散过程时先前用于确定性概率流的向量场（Song等（2020b），方程13）一致；详见附录D。然而，将扩散条件向量场与流匹配目标结合，提供了一种有吸引力的训练替代方案——我们在实验中发现其比现有的得分匹配方法更稳定且更鲁棒。

Another important observation is that, as these probability paths were previously derived as solutions of diffusion processes, they do not actually reach a true noise distribution in finite time. In practice, p0(x) is simply approximated by a suitable Gaussian distribution for sampling and likelihood evaluation. Instead, our construction provides full control over the probability path, and we can just directly set μt and σt ,as we will do next.

另一个重要观察是，由于这些概率路径先前是作为扩散过程的解导出的，它们实际上在有限时间内并未达到真正的噪声分布。实际上，p0(x)通常通过合适的高斯分布进行近似，用于采样和似然评估。相反，我们的构造提供了对概率路径的完全控制，我们可以直接设置μt和σt，正如接下来所做的那样。

Example II: Optimal Transport conditional VFs. An arguably more natural choice for conditional probability paths is to define the mean and the std to simply change linearly in time, i.e.,

例子二：最优传输条件向量场。一个更自然的条件概率路径选择是定义均值和标准差随时间线性变化，即

(20)μt(x)=tx1,andσt(x)=1−(1−σmin)t.

According to Theorem 3 this path is generated by the VF

根据定理3，该路径由向量场生成

(21)ut(x∣x1)=x1−(1−σmin)x1−(1−σmin)t,

Figure 2: Compared to the diffusion path's conditional score function, the OT path's conditional vector field has constant direction in time and is arguably simpler to fit with a parametric model. Note the blue color denotes larger magnitude while red color denotes smaller magnitude.

图2：与扩散路径的条件得分函数相比，最优传输路径的条件向量场在时间上方向恒定，且更易于用参数模型拟合。注意蓝色表示较大幅值，红色表示较小幅值。

which,in contrast to the diffusion conditional VF (equation 19),is defined for all t∈[0,1] . The conditional flow that corresponds to ut(x∣x1) is

与扩散条件向量场（方程19）不同，该向量场定义于所有t∈[0,1]。对应于ut(x∣x1)的条件流为

(22)ψt(x)=(1−(1−σmin)t)x+tx1,

and in this case, the CFM loss (see equations 9, 14) takes the form:

在此情况下，CFM损失（见方程9，14）形式为：

(23)LCFM(θ)=Et,q(x1),p(x0)‖vt(ψt(x0))−(x1−(1−σmin)x0)‖2.

Allowing the mean and std to change linearly not only leads to simple and intuitive paths, but it is actually also optimal in the following sense. The conditional flow ψt(x) is in fact the Optimal Transport (OT) displacement map between the two Gaussians p0(x∣x1) and p1(x∣x1) . The OT interpolant, which is a probability path, is defined to be (see Definition 1.1 in McCann (1997)):

允许均值和标准差线性变化不仅导致简单直观的路径，而且实际上在以下意义上也是最优的。条件流ψt(x)实际上是两个高斯分布p0(x∣x1)和p1(x∣x1)之间的最优传输（Optimal Transport, OT）位移映射。OT插值，即概率路径，定义为（参见McCann (1997)中的定义1.1）：

(24)pt=[(1−t)id+tψ]⋆p0

where ψ:Rd→Rd is the OT map pushing p0 to p1 ,id denotes the identity map,i.e., id(x)=x , and (1−t)id+tψ is called the OT displacement map. Example 1.7 in McCann (1997) shows,that in our case of two Gaussians where the first is a standard one, the OT displacement map takes the form of equation 22 .

其中ψ:Rd→Rd是将p0推送到p1的OT映射，id表示恒等映射，即id(x)=x，而(1−t)id+tψ称为OT位移映射。McCann (1997)中的例1.7表明，在我们考虑的两个高斯分布中，第一个为标准高斯，OT位移映射呈现方程22的形式。

Figure 3: Diffusion and OT trajectories.

图3：扩散和OT轨迹。

Intuitively, particles under the OT displacement map always move in straight line trajectories and with constant speed. Figure 3 depicts sampling paths for the diffusion and OT conditional VFs. Interestingly, we find that sampling trajectory from diffusion paths can "overshoot" the final sample, resulting in unnecessary backtracking, whilst the OT paths are guaranteed to stay straight.

直观地，粒子在OT位移映射下总是沿直线轨迹以恒定速度移动。图3展示了扩散和OT条件向量场的采样路径。有趣的是，我们发现扩散路径的采样轨迹可能会“超越”最终样本，导致不必要的回溯，而OT路径则保证保持直线。

Figure 2 compares the diffusion conditional score function (the regression target in a typical diffusion methods),i.e., ∇log⁡pt(x∣x1) with pt defined as in equation 18, with the OT conditional VF (equation 21). The start (p0) and end (p1) Gaussians are identical in both examples. An interesting observation is that the OT VF has a constant direction in time, which arguably leads to a simpler regression task. This property can also be verified directly from equation 21 as the VF can be written in the form ut(x∣x1)=g(t)h(x∣x1) . Figure 8 in the Appendix shows a visualization of the Diffusion VF. Lastly, we note that although the conditional flow is optimal, this by no means imply that the marginal VF is an optimal transport solution. Nevertheless, we expect the marginal vector field to remain relatively simple.

图2比较了扩散条件得分函数（典型扩散方法中的回归目标），即方程18中定义的∇log⁡pt(x∣x1)与OT条件向量场（方程21）。起始高斯(p0)和终止高斯(p1)在两个例子中均相同。一个有趣的观察是，OT向量场在时间上方向恒定，这无疑使回归任务更简单。该性质也可直接从方程21验证，因为向量场可写成ut(x∣x1)=g(t)h(x∣x1)的形式。附录中的图8展示了扩散向量场的可视化。最后，我们注意到尽管条件流是最优的，但这并不意味着边缘向量场是最优传输解。然而，我们预计边缘向量场仍将保持相对简单。

5 RELATED WORK

5 相关工作

Continuous Normalizing Flows were introduced in (Chen et al., 2018) as a continuous-time version of Normalizing Flows (see e.g., Kobyzev et al. (2020); Papamakarios et al. (2021) for an overview). Originally, CNFs are trained with the maximum likelihood objective, but this involves expensive ODE simulations for the forward and backward propagation, resulting in high time complexity due to the sequential nature of ODE simulations. Although some works demonstrated the capability of CNF generative models for image synthesis (Grathwohl et al., 2018), scaling up to very high dimensional images is inherently difficult. A number of works attempted to regularize the ODE to be easier to solve, e.g., using augmentation (Dupont et al., 2019), adding regularization terms (Yang & Karniadakis, 2019; Finlay et al., 2020; Onken et al., 2021; Tong et al., 2020; Kelly et al., 2020), or stochastically sampling the integration interval (Du et al., 2022). These works merely aim to regularize the ODE but do not change the fundamental training algorithm. In order to speed up CNF training, some works have developed simulation-free CNF training frameworks by explicitly designing the target probability path and the dynamics. For instance, Rozen et al. (2021) consider a linear interpolation between the prior and the target density but involves integrals that were difficult to estimate in high dimensions, while Ben-Hamu et al. (2022) consider general probability paths similar to this work but suffers from biased gradients in the stochastic minibatch regime. In contrast, the Flow Matching framework allows simulation-free training with unbiased gradients and readily scales to very high dimensions.

连续归一化流（Continuous Normalizing Flows, CNFs）由(Chen et al., 2018)提出，作为归一化流（Normalizing Flows）的连续时间版本（参见如Kobyzev et al. (2020); Papamakarios et al. (2021)的综述）。最初，CNFs通过最大似然目标进行训练，但这涉及正向和反向传播的昂贵常微分方程（ODE）模拟，由于ODE模拟的顺序性质，导致时间复杂度较高。尽管一些工作展示了CNF生成模型在图像合成中的能力（Grathwohl et al., 2018），但扩展到非常高维图像本质上仍然困难。许多工作尝试通过正则化ODE使其更易求解，例如使用增强（Dupont et al., 2019）、添加正则项（Yang & Karniadakis, 2019; Finlay et al., 2020; Onken et al., 2021; Tong et al., 2020; Kelly et al., 2020）或随机采样积分区间（Du et al., 2022）。这些工作仅旨在正则化ODE，但未改变基本训练算法。为加速CNF训练，一些工作通过显式设计目标概率路径和动力学，开发了无模拟的CNF训练框架。例如，Rozen et al. (2021)考虑了先验和目标密度之间的线性插值，但涉及难以在高维估计的积分，而Ben-Hamu et al. (2022)考虑了类似本工作的通用概率路径，但在随机小批量 regime 中存在偏差梯度。相比之下，Flow Matching框架允许无模拟训练，具有无偏梯度，并且易于扩展到非常高维。

Figure 4: (left) Trajectories of CNFs trained with different objectives on 2D checkerboard data. The OT path introduces the checkerboard pattern much earlier, while FM results in more stable training. (right) FM with OT results in more efficient sampling, solved using the midpoint scheme.

图4：（左）在二维棋盘格数据上使用不同目标训练的CNFs轨迹。OT路径更早引入棋盘格模式，而FM则带来更稳定的训练。（右）结合OT的FM实现了更高效的采样，采用中点法求解。

Another approach to simulation-free training relies on the construction of a diffusion process to indirectly define the target probability path (Sohl-Dickstein et al., 2015; Ho et al., 2020; Song & Ermon, 2019). Song et al. (2020b) shows that diffusion models are trained using denoising score matching (Vincent, 2011), a conditional objective that provides unbiased gradients with respect to the score matching objective. Conditional Flow Matching draws inspiration from this result, but generalizes to matching vector fields directly. Due to the ease of scalability, diffusion models have received increased attention, producing a variety of improvements such as loss-rescaling (Song et al., 2021), adding classifier guidance along with architectural improvements (Dhariwal & Nichol, 2021), and learning the noise schedule (Nichol & Dhariwal, 2021; Kingma et al., 2021). However, (Nichol & Dhariwal, 2021) and (Kingma et al., 2021) only consider a restricted setting of Gaussian conditional paths defined by simple diffusion processes with a single parameter-in particular, it does not include our conditional OT path. In an another line of works, (De Bortoli et al., 2021; Wang et al., 2021; Peluchetti, 2021) proposed finite time diffusion constructions via diffusion bridges theory resolving the approximation error incurred by infinite time denoising constructions. While existing works make use of a connection between diffusion processes and continuous normalizing flows with the same probability path (Maoutsa et al., 2020b; Song et al., 2020b; 2021), our work allows us to generalize beyond the class of probability paths modeled by simple diffusion. With our work, it is possible to completely sidestep the diffusion process construction and reason directly with probability paths, while still retaining efficient training and log-likelihood evaluations. Lastly, concurrently to our work (Liu et al., 2022; Albergo & Vanden-Eijnden, 2022) arrived at similar conditional objectives for simulation-free training of CNFs, while Neklyudov et al. (2023) derived an implicit objective when ut is assumed to be a gradient field.

另一种无模拟训练方法依赖于构建扩散过程以间接定义目标概率路径（Sohl-Dickstein等，2015；Ho等，2020；Song & Ermon，2019）。Song等（2020b）表明扩散模型通过去噪得分匹配（Vincent，2011）进行训练，这是一种条件目标，提供了相对于得分匹配目标的无偏梯度。条件流匹配（Conditional Flow Matching）借鉴了这一结果，但推广为直接匹配向量场。由于易于扩展，扩散模型受到更多关注，产生了多种改进，如损失重标定（Song等，2021）、结合分类器引导及架构改进（Dhariwal & Nichol，2021）、以及学习噪声调度（Nichol & Dhariwal，2021；Kingma等，2021）。然而，（Nichol & Dhariwal，2021）和（Kingma等，2021）仅考虑由单参数简单扩散过程定义的高斯条件路径，特别是不包括我们的条件OT路径。在另一系列工作中，（De Bortoli等，2021；Wang等，2021；Peluchetti，2021）通过扩散桥理论提出了有限时间扩散构造，解决了无限时间去噪构造带来的近似误差。尽管现有工作利用了扩散过程与具有相同概率路径的连续归一化流之间的联系（Maoutsa等，2020b；Song等，2020b；2021），我们的工作使得超越简单扩散建模的概率路径类别成为可能。通过我们的工作，可以完全绕过扩散过程构造，直接处理概率路径，同时仍保持高效训练和对数似然评估。最后，与我们工作同时进行的（Liu等，2022；Albergo & Vanden-Eijnden，2022）提出了类似的条件目标用于CNFs的无模拟训练，而Neklyudov等（2023）在假设ut为梯度场时推导出了隐式目标。

6 EXPERIMENTS

6 实验

We explore the empirical benefits of using Flow Matching on the image datasets of CIFAR- 10 (Krizhevsky et al., 2009) and ImageNet at resolutions 32, 64, and 128 (Chrabaszcz et al., 2017; Deng et al., 2009). We also ablate the choice of diffusion path in Flow Matching, particularly between the standard variance preserving diffusion path and the optimal transport path. We discuss how sample generation is improved by directly parameterizing the generating vector field and using the Flow Matching objective. Lastly we show Flow Matching can also be used in the conditional generation setting. Unless otherwise specified, we evaluate likelihood and samples from the model using dopri5 (Dormand & Prince, 1980) at absolute and relative tolerances of 1e-5. Generated samples can be found in the Appendix, and all implementation details are in Appendix E.

我们在CIFAR-10（Krizhevsky等，2009）和分辨率为32、64及128的ImageNet（Chrabaszcz等，2017；Deng等，2009）图像数据集上探讨了使用流匹配（Flow Matching）的经验优势。我们还对流匹配中扩散路径的选择进行了消融实验，特别是在标准方差保持扩散路径和最优传输路径之间。我们讨论了通过直接参数化生成向量场并使用流匹配目标，样本生成如何得到改进。最后，我们展示了流匹配也可用于条件生成设置。除非另有说明，我们使用dopri5（Dormand & Prince，1980）以绝对和相对容差1e-5评估模型的似然和样本。生成样本见附录，所有实现细节见附录E。

6.1 Density Modeling and Sample Quality on ImageNet

6.1 ImageNet上的密度建模与样本质量

We start by comparing the same model architecture, i.e., the U-Net architecture from Dhariwal & Nichol (2021) with minimal changes, trained on CIFAR-10, and ImageNet 32/64 with different popular diffusion-based losses: DDPM from (Ho et al., 2020), Score Matching (SM) (Song et al., 2020b), and Score Flow (SF) (Song et al., 2021); see Appendix E. 1 for exact details. Table 1 (left) summarizes our results alongside these baselines reporting negative log-likelihood (NLL) in units of bits per dimension (BPD), sample quality as measured by the Frechet Inception Distance (FID; Heusel et al. (2017)), and averaged number of function evaluations (NFE) required for the adaptive solver to reach its a prespecified numerical tolerance,averaged over 50k samples. All models are trained using the same architecture, hyperparameter values and number of training iterations, where baselines are allowed more iterations for better convergence. Note that these are unconditional models. On both CIFAR-10 and ImageNet, FM-OT consistently obtains best results across all our quantitative measures compared to competing methods. We are noticing a higher that usual FID performance in CIFAR-10 compared to previous works (Ho et al., 2020; Song et al., 2020b; 2021) that can possibly be explained by the fact that our used architecture was not optimized for CIFAR-10.

我们首先比较相同的模型架构，即Dhariwal & Nichol (2021)提出的U-Net架构，几乎未做修改，分别在CIFAR-10和ImageNet 32/64上使用不同流行的基于扩散的损失函数训练：DDPM（Ho等，2020）、得分匹配（Score Matching, SM）（Song等，2020b）和得分流（Score Flow, SF）（Song等，2021）；具体细节见附录E.1。表1（左）总结了我们的结果及这些基线，报告了以每维比特数（bits per dimension, BPD）为单位的负对数似然（NLL）、以Frechet Inception距离（FID；Heusel等，2017）衡量的样本质量，以及自适应求解器达到预设数值容差所需的平均函数评估次数（NFE），均基于50k个样本平均。所有模型均使用相同架构、超参数和训练迭代次数，基线方法允许更多迭代以获得更好收敛。注意这些均为无条件模型。在CIFAR-10和ImageNet上，FM-OT在所有定量指标上均优于竞争方法。我们注意到CIFAR-10上的FID表现较以往工作（Ho等，2020；Song等，2020b；2021）更高，这可能是因为我们使用的架构未针对CIFAR-10进行优化。

Secondly, Table 1 (right) compares a model trained using Flow Matching with the OT path on Ima-geNet at resolution 128×128 . Our FID is state-of-the-art with the exception of IC-GAN (Casanova et al., 2021) which uses conditioning with a self-supervised ResNet50 model, and therefore is left out of this table. Figures 11, 12, 13 in the Appendix show non-curated samples from these models.

其次，表1（右）比较了在ImageNet分辨率128×128上使用流匹配与OT路径训练的模型。我们的FID达到最先进水平，除IC-GAN（Casanova等，2021）外，该方法使用自监督ResNet50模型进行条件生成，因此未列入本表。附录中的图11、12、13展示了这些模型的非筛选样本。

Faster training. While existing works train diffusion models with a very high number of iterations (e.g., 1.3m and 10m iterations are reported by Score Flow and VDM, respectively), we find that Flow Matching generally converges much faster. Figure 5 shows FID curves during training of Flow Matching and all baselines for ImageNet 64×64 ; FM-OT is able to lower the FID faster and to a greater extent than the alternatives. For ImageNet-128 Dhariwal &Nichol (2021) train for 4.36m iterations with batch size 256, while FM (with 25% larger model) used 500k iterations with batch size 1.5k ,i.e., 33% less image throughput; see Table 3 for exact details. Furthermore, the cost of sampling from a model can drastically change during training for score matching, whereas the sampling cost stays constant when training with Flow Matching (Figure 10 in Appendix).

训练更快。现有工作通常使用极高的迭代次数训练扩散模型（例如，Score Flow和VDM分别报告了1.3m和10m次迭代），而我们发现流匹配通常收敛更快。图5展示了ImageNet 64×64上流匹配及所有基线的训练期间FID曲线；FM-OT能够更快且更大幅度地降低FID。对于ImageNet-128，Dhariwal & Nichol (2021)使用批量大小256训练了4.36m次迭代，而FM（模型规模大25%）使用批量大小1.5k训练了500k次迭代，即图像吞吐量减少了33%；具体见表3。此外，得分匹配训练过程中采样成本可能大幅变化，而流匹配训练时采样成本保持恒定（附录图10）。

Figure 5: Image quality during training,ImageNet 64×64 .

图5：训练期间的图像质量，ImageNet 64×64。

6.2 SAMPLING EFFICIENCY

6.2 采样效率

For sampling,we first draw a random noise sample x0∼N(0,I) then compute ϕ1(x0) by solving equation 1 with the trained VF, vt ,on the interval t∈[0,1] using an ODE solver. While diffusion models can also be sampled through an SDE formulation, this can be highly inefficient and many methods that propose fast samplers (e.g., Song et al. (2020a); Zhang & Chen (2022)) directly make use of the ODE perspective (see Appendix D). In part, this is due to ODE solvers being much more efficient-yielding lower error at similar computational costs (Kloeden et al., 2012)- and the multitude of available ODE solver schemes. When compared to our ablation models, we find that models trained using Flow Matching with the OT path always result in the most efficient sampler, regardless of ODE solver, as demonstrated next.

对于采样，我们首先绘制一个随机噪声样本x0∼N(0,I)，然后通过使用训练好的VF（值函数）vt，在区间t∈[0,1]上利用ODE求解器求解方程1来计算ϕ1(x0)。虽然扩散模型也可以通过随机微分方程（SDE）形式进行采样，但这通常效率较低，许多提出快速采样方法的研究（例如，Song等人（2020a）；Zhang & Chen（2022））直接采用ODE视角（见附录D）。部分原因在于ODE求解器效率更高——在相似计算成本下误差更低（Kloeden等，2012）——且存在多种可用的ODE求解方案。与我们的消融模型相比，我们发现使用最优传输（OT）路径训练的Flow Matching模型无论采用何种ODE求解器，始终能实现最高效的采样器，具体如下所示。

Figure 7: Flow Matching, especially when using OT paths, allows us to use fewer evaluations for sampling while retaining similar numerical error (left) and sample quality (right). Results are shown for models trained on ImageNet 32×32 ,and numerical errors are for the midpoint scheme.

图7：Flow Matching，尤其是在使用OT路径时，使我们能够减少采样评估次数，同时保持相似的数值误差（左图）和样本质量（右图）。结果展示了在ImageNet32×32上训练的模型，数值误差采用中点法方案计算。

Sample paths. We first qualitatively visualize the difference in sampling paths between diffusion and OT. Figure 6 shows samples from ImageNet-64 models using identical random seeds, where we find that the OT path model starts generating images sooner than the diffusion path models, where noise dominates the image until the very last time point. We additionally depict the probability density paths in 2D generation of a checkerboard pattern, Figure 4 (left), noticing a similar trend.

采样路径。我们首先定性地可视化扩散路径与OT路径之间的采样差异。图6展示了使用相同随机种子的ImageNet-64模型样本，发现OT路径模型比扩散路径模型更早开始生成图像，而扩散路径模型直到最后时刻噪声仍主导图像。我们还展示了二维生成棋盘图案的概率密度路径（图4左），观察到类似趋势。

Low-cost samples. We next switch to fixed-step solvers and compare low (≤100) NFE samples computed with the ImageNet-32 models from Table 1. In Figure 7 (left), we compare the per-pixel MSE of low NFE solutions compared with 1000 NFE solutions (we use 256 random noise seeds), and notice that the FM with OT model produces the best numerical error, in terms of computational cost,requiring roughly only 60% of the NFEs to reach the same error threshold as diffusion models. Secondly, Figure 7 (right) shows how FID changes as a result of the computational cost, where we find FM with OT is able to achieve decent FID even at very low NFE values, producing better tradeoff between sample quality and cost compared to ablated models. Figure 4 (right) shows low-cost sampling effects for the 2D checkerboard experiment.

低成本样本。接下来我们切换到固定步长求解器，比较表1中ImageNet-32模型计算的低(≤100) NFE样本。在图7（左）中，我们比较了低NFE解与1000 NFE解的每像素均方误差（MSE）（使用256个随机噪声种子），注意到采用OT路径的FM模型在计算成本方面产生了最佳数值误差，达到相同误差阈值所需的NFE约为扩散模型的60%。其次，图7（右）展示了FID随计算成本的变化，发现FM-OT即使在极低NFE值下也能实现较好的FID，在样本质量与成本之间实现了比消融模型更优的权衡。图4（右）展示了二维棋盘实验的低成本采样效果。

6.3 CONDITIONAL SAMPLING FROM LOW-RESOLUTION IMAGES

6.3 从低分辨率图像进行条件采样

Lastly, we experimented with Flow Matching for conditional image generation. In particular, upsampling images from 64×64 to 256×256 . We follow the evaluation procedure in (Saharia et al., 2022) and compute the FID of the upsampled validation images; baselines include reference (FID of original validation set), and regression. Results are in Table 2. Upsampled image samples are shown in Figures 14, 15 in the Appendix. FM-OT achieves similar PSNR and SSIM values to (Saharia et al., 2022) while considerably improving on FID and IS, which as argued by (Saharia et al., 2022) is a better indication of generation quality.

最后，我们尝试了Flow Matching用于条件图像生成，特别是将图像从64×64上采样到256×256。我们遵循（Saharia等，2022）中的评估流程，计算上采样验证图像的FID；基线包括参考（原始验证集的FID）和回归方法。结果见表2。上采样图像样本展示于附录图14、15。FM-OT在PSNR和SSIM指标上与（Saharia等，2022）相当，同时在FID和IS上有显著提升，正如（Saharia等，2022）所论述，这更能反映生成质量。

7 CONCLUSION

7 结论

We introduced Flow Matching, a new simulation-free framework for training Continuous Normalizing Flow models, relying on conditional constructions to effortlessly scale to very high dimensions. Furthermore, the FM framework provides an alternative view on diffusion models, and suggests forsaking the stochastic/diffusion construction in favor of more directly specifying the probability path, allowing us to, e.g., construct paths that allow faster sampling and/or improve generation. We experimentally showed the ease of training and sampling when using the Flow Matching framework, and in the future, we expect FM to open the door to allowing a multitude of probability paths (e.g., non-isotropic Gaussians or more general kernels altogether).

我们提出了Flow Matching，一种无需模拟的新框架，用于训练连续归一化流（Continuous Normalizing Flow）模型，依赖条件构造轻松扩展到极高维度。此外，FM框架为扩散模型提供了另一种视角，建议放弃随机/扩散构造，转而更直接地指定概率路径，从而允许我们构建如更快采样和/或改进生成的路径。我们通过实验展示了使用Flow Matching框架训练和采样的简便性，未来我们期望FM能开启多种概率路径的大门（例如，非各向同性高斯或更通用的核函数）。

8 SOCIAL RESPONSIBILITY

8 社会责任

Along side its many positive applications, image generation can also be used for harmful proposes. Using content-controlled training sets and image validation/classification can help reduce these uses. Furthermore, the energy demand for training large deep learning models is increasing at a rapid pace (Amodei et al., 2018; Thompson et al., 2020), focusing on methods that are able to train using less gradient updates / image throughput can lead to significant time and energy savings. B THE CONTINUITY EQUATION

B 连续性方程

One method of testing if a vector field vt generates a probability path pt is the continuity equation (Villani, 2009). It is a Partial Differential Equation (PDE) providing a necessary and sufficient condition to ensuring that a vector field vt generates pt ,

检验向量场vt是否生成概率路径pt的一种方法是连续性方程（Villani，2009）。它是一个偏微分方程（PDE），提供了向量场vt生成pt的必要且充分条件，

(26)ddtpt(x)+div(pt(x)vt(x))=0,

where the divergence operator,div,is defined with respect to the spatial variable x=(x1,…,xd) , i.e., div=∑i=1d⁡∂∂xi .

其中散度算子div是相对于空间变量x=(x1,…,xd)定义的，即div=∑i=1d⁡∂∂xi。

C COMPUTING PROBABILITIES OF THE CNF MODEL

C 计算CNF模型的概率

We are given an arbitrary data point x1∈Rd and need to compute the model probability at that point,i.e., p1(x1) . Below we recap how this can be done covering the basic relevant ODEs,the scaling of the divergence computation, taking into account data transformations (e.g., centering of data), and Bits-Per-Dimension computation.

给定任意数据点x1∈Rd，需要计算该点处的模型概率，即p1(x1)。下面我们回顾如何完成此计算，涵盖相关的基本常微分方程（ODE）、散度计算的缩放、考虑数据变换（如数据中心化）以及每维比特数（Bits-Per-Dimension）的计算。

ODE for computing p1(x1) The continuity equation with equation 1 lead to the instantaneous change of variable (Chen et al., 2018; Ben-Hamu et al., 2022):

用于计算p1(x1)的ODE 连续性方程与方程1结合，导出变量瞬时变化（Chen等，2018；Ben-Hamu等，2022）：

ddtlog⁡pt(ϕt(x))+div(vt(ϕt(x))=0.

Integrating t∈[0,1] gives:

对t∈[0,1]积分得到：

(27)log⁡p1(ϕ1(x))−log⁡p0(ϕ0(x))=−∫01div(vt(ϕt(x)))dt

Therefore, the log probability can be computed together with the flow trajectory by solving the ODE:

因此，概率的对数可以通过求解ODE与流轨迹同时计算：

(28)ddt[ϕt(x)f(t)]=[vt(ϕt(x))−div(vt(ϕt(x)))]

Given initial conditions

给定初始条件

(29)[ϕ0(x)f(0)]=[x0c].

the solution [ϕt(x),f(t)]T is uniquely defined (up to some mild conditions on the VF vt ). Denote x1=ϕ1(x) ,and according to equation 27,

解[ϕt(x),f(t)]T在一定条件下（对向量场vt的温和约束）唯一确定。记作x1=ϕ1(x)，根据方程27，

(30)f(1)=c+log⁡p1(x1)−log⁡p0(x0).

Now,we are given an arbitrary x1 and want to compute p1(x1) . For this end,we will need to solve equation 28 in reverse. That is,

现在，给定任意x1，希望计算p1(x1)。为此，需要反向求解方程28，即

(31)dds[ϕ1−s(x)f(1−s)]=[−v1−s(ϕ1−s(x))div(v1−s(ϕ1−s(x)))]

and we solve this equation for s∈[0,1] with the initial conditions at s=0 :

并以方程29中的初始条件在s=0处求解该方程的s∈[0,1]：

(32)[ϕ1(x)f(1)]=[x10].

From uniqueness of ODEs, the solution will be identical to the solution of equation 28 with initial conditions in equation 29 where c=log⁡p0(x0)−log⁡p1(x1) . This can be seen from equation 30 and setting f(1)=0 . Therefore we get that

根据ODE的唯一性，解将与方程28在方程29初始条件下的解相同，其中c=log⁡p0(x0)−log⁡p1(x1)。此结论可由方程30并设定f(1)=0得出。因此得到

f(0)=log⁡p0(x0)−log⁡p1(x1)

and consequently

进而

(33)log⁡p1(x1)=log⁡p0(x0)−f(0).

To summarize,to compute p1(x1) we first solve the ODE in equation 31 with initial conditions in equation 32 , and the compute equation 33 .

总结而言，计算p1(x1)时，先求解方程31的ODE，初始条件见方程32，然后计算方程33。

Unbiased estimator to p1(x1) Solving equation 31 requires computation of div of VFs in Rd which is costly. Grathwohl et al. (2018) suggest to replace the divergence by the (unbiased) Hutchinson trace estimator,

对p1(x1)的无偏估计器 求解方程31需要计算向量场Rd的散度，计算成本较高。Grathwohl等（2018）建议用（无偏）Hutchinson迹估计器替代散度，

(34)dds[ϕ1−s(x)f~(1−s)]=[−v1−s(ϕ1−s(x))zTDv1−s(ϕ1−s(x))z],

where z∈Rd is a sample from a random variable such that EzzT=I . Solving the ODE in equation 34 exactly (in practice, with a small controlled error) with initial conditions in equation 32 leads to

=log⁡p0(x0)−(f(0)−f(1))

=log⁡p1(x1),

where in the third equality we switched order of integration assuming the sufficient condition of Fubini's theorem hold, and in the previous to last equality we used equation 30 . Therefore the random variable

在第三个等式中，我们交换了积分顺序，假设满足Fubini定理的充分条件；在倒数第二个等式中，使用了方程30。因此随机变量

(35)log⁡p0(x0)−f~(0)

is an unbiased estimator for log⁡p1(x1) . To summarize,for a scalable unbiased estimation of p1(x1) we first solve the ODE in equation 34 with initial conditions in equation 32 , and then output equation 35.

是log⁡p1(x1)的无偏估计器。总结，为了可扩展的无偏估计p1(x1)，先求解方程34的ODE，初始条件见方程32，然后输出方程35。

Transformed data Often, before training our generative model we transform the data, e.g., we scale and/or translate the data. Such a transformation is denoted by φ−1:Rd→Rd and our generative model becomes a composition

变换后的数据 通常，在训练我们的生成模型之前，我们会对数据进行变换，例如对数据进行缩放和/或平移。这样的变换记作φ−1:Rd→Rd，我们的生成模型则变为一个复合模型

ψ(x)=φ∘ϕ(x)

where ϕ:Rd→Rd is the model we train. Given a prior probability p0 we have that the push forward of this probability under ψ (equation 3 and equation 4) takes the form

其中ϕ:Rd→Rd是我们训练的模型。给定先验概率p0，该概率在ψ下的推前（push forward）（见公式3和公式4）形式为

p1(x)=ψ∗p0(x)=p0(ϕ−1(φ−1(x)))det[Dϕ−1(φ−1(x))]det[Dφ−1(x)]

=(ϕ∗p0(φ−1(x)))det[Dφ−1(x)]

and therefore

因此

log⁡p1(x)=log⁡ϕ∗p0(φ−1(x))+log⁡det[Dφ−1(x)].

For images d=H×W×3 and we consider a transform ϕ that maps each pixel value from [−1,1] to [0,256] . Therefore,

对于图像d=H×W×3，我们考虑一个变换ϕ，将每个像素值从[−1,1]映射到[0,256]。因此，

For this case we have

每维比特数（Bits-Per-Dimension，BPD）计算，BPD定义为

(37)BPD=Ex1[−log2p1(x1)d]=Ex1[−log⁡p1(x1)dlog⁡2]

and log⁡ϕ∗p0(φ−1(x)) is approximated using the unbiased estimator in equation 35 over the transformed data φ−1(x1) . Averaging the unbiased estimator on a large test test x1 provides a good approximation to the test set BPD.

D DIFFUSION CONDITIONAL VECTOR FIELDS

D 扩散条件向量场

We derive the vector field governing the Probability Flow ODE (equation 13 in Song et al. (2020b)) for the VE and VP diffusion paths (equation 18) and note that it coincides with the conditional vector fields we derive using Theorem 3, namely the vector fields defined in equations 16 and 19 .

我们推导了控制概率流常微分方程（Song等人(2020b)中公式13）中VE和VP扩散路径（公式18）的向量场，并注意到它与我们使用定理3推导的条件向量场一致，即公式16和19中定义的向量场。

We start with a short primer on how to find a conditional vector field for the probability path described by the Fokker-Planck equation, then instantiate it for the VE and VP probability paths.

我们首先简要介绍如何为由Fokker-Planck方程描述的概率路径找到条件向量场，然后将其应用于VE和VP概率路径。

Since in the diffusion literature the diffusion process runs from data at time t=0 to noise at time t=1 ,we will need the following lemma to translate the diffusion VFs to our convention of t=0 corresponds to noise and t=1 corresponds to data:

由于扩散文献中扩散过程是从时间t=0的数据到时间t=1的噪声，我们需要以下引理将扩散向量场转换为我们的约定，即t=0对应噪声，t=1对应数据：

Lemma 1. Consider a flow defined by a vector field ut(x) generating probability density path pt(x) . Then,the vector field u~t(x)=−u1−t(x) generates the path p~t(x)=p1−t(x) when initiated from p~0(x)=p1(x) .

引理1. 考虑由向量场ut(x)定义的流，生成概率密度路径pt(x)。则向量场u~t(x)=−u1−t(x)在初始于p~0(x)=p1(x)时生成路径p~t(x)=p1−t(x)。

Proof. We use the continuity equation (equation 26):

证明. 我们使用连续性方程（公式26）：

ddtp~t(x)=ddtp1−t(x)=−p1−t′(x)

=div(p1−t(x)u1−t(x))

=−div(p~t(x)(−u1−t(x)))

and therefore u~t(x)=−u1−t(x) generates p~t(x) .

因此u~t(x)=−u1−t(x)生成了p~t(x)。

Conditional VFs for Fokker-Planck probability paths Consider a Stochastic Differential Equation (SDE) of the standard form

Fokker-Planck概率路径的条件向量场，考虑标准形式的随机微分方程（SDE）

(38)dy=ftdt+gtdw

with time parameter t ,drift ft ,diffusion coefficient gt ,and dw is the Wiener process. The solution yt to the SDE is a stochastic process, i.e., a continuous time-dependent random variable, the probability density of which, pt(yt) ,is characterized by the Fokker-Planck equation:

时间参数为t，漂移项为ft，扩散系数为gt，dw为Wiener过程。该SDE的解yt是一个随机过程，即连续时间依赖的随机变量，其概率密度pt(yt)由Fokker-Planck方程描述：

(39)dptdt=−div(ftpt)+gt22Δpt

where Δ represents the Laplace operator (in y ),namely div∇ ,where ∇ is the gradient operator (also in y ). Rewriting this equation in the form of the continuity equation can be done as follows (Maoutsa et al., 2020a):

其中 Δ 表示拉普拉斯算子（Laplace operator）（在 y 中），即 div∇，其中 ∇ 是梯度算子（gradient operator）（同样在 y 中）。将该方程重写为连续性方程的形式如下（Maoutsa 等，2020a）：

dptdt=−div(ftpt−g22∇ptptpt)=−div((ft−gt22∇log⁡pt)pt)=−div(wtpt)

where the vector field

其中向量场

(40)wt=ft−gt22∇log⁡pt

satisfies the continuity equation with the probability path pt ,and therefore generates pt .

满足带有概率路径 pt 的连续性方程，因此生成 pt。

Variance Exploding (VE) path The SDE for the VE path is

方差爆炸（Variance Exploding, VE）路径 VE路径的随机微分方程（SDE）为

dy=ddtσt2dw

where σ0=0 and increasing to infinity as t→1 . The SDE is moving from data, y0 ,at t=0 to noise, y1 ,at t=1 with the probability path

其中 σ0=0 并且随着 t→1 增大趋向无穷。该SDE从数据 y0（在 t=0 时刻）向噪声 y1（在 t=1 时刻）演化，其概率路径为

pt(y∣y0)=N(y∣y0,σt2I).

The conditional VF according to equation 40 is:

根据方程40，条件向量场（VF）为：

wt(y∣y0)=σt′σt(y−y0)

Using Lemma 1 we get that the probability path

利用引理1，我们得到概率路径

p~t(y∣y0)=N(y∣y0,σ1−t2I)

is generated by

由以下方程生成

w~t(y∣y0)=−σ1−t′σ1−t(y−y0),

which coincides with equation 17 .

与方程17一致。

Variance Preserving (VP) path The SDE for the VP path is

方差保持（Variance Preserving, VP）路径 VP路径的随机微分方程（SDE）为

dy=−T′(t)2y+T′(t)dw,

where T(t)=∫0tβ(s)ds,t∈[0,1] . The SDE coefficients are therefore

其中 T(t)=∫0tβ(s)ds,t∈[0,1]。因此，SDE的系数为

fs(y)=−T′(s)2y,gs=T′(s)

and

和

pt(y∣y0)=N(y∣e−12T(t)y0,(1−e−T(t))I).

Plugging these choices in equation 40 we get the conditional VF

将这些选项代入方程40，我们得到条件向量场

(41)wt(y∣y0)=T′(t)2(y−e−12T(t)y01−e−T(t)−y)

Using Lemma 1 to reverse the time we get the conditional VF for the reverse probability path:

利用引理1进行时间反转，我们得到逆概率路径的条件向量场：

w~t(y∣y0)=−T′(1−t)2(y−e−12T(1−t)y01−e−T(1−t)−y)

=−T′(1−t)2[e−T(1−t)y−e−12T(1−t)y01−e−T(1−t)],

which coincides with equation 19.

与方程19一致。

E IMPLEMENTATION DETAILS

E 实现细节

For the 2D example we used an MLP with 5-layers of 512 neurons each, while for images we used the UNet architecture from Dhariwal & Nichol (2021). For images, we center crop images and resize to the appropriate dimension,whereas for the 32×32 and 64×64 resolutions we use the same pre-processing as (Chrabaszcz et al., 2017). The three methods (FM-OT, FM-Diffusion, and SM-Diffusion) are always trained on the same architecture, same hyper-parameters, and for the same number of epochs.

对于二维示例，我们使用了一个包含5层、每层512个神经元的多层感知机（MLP），而对于图像则采用了Dhariwal & Nichol（2021）提出的UNet架构。对于图像，我们先进行中心裁剪并调整到合适的尺寸，而对于32×32和64×64分辨率，则采用了与（Chrabaszcz等，2017）相同的预处理方法。三种方法（FM-OT、FM-Diffusion和SM-Diffusion）均在相同架构、相同超参数和相同训练轮数下训练。

E.2 TRAINING & EVALUATION DETAILS

E.2 训练与评估细节

We report the hyper-parameters used in Table 3. We use full 32 bit-precision for training CIFAR10 and ImageNet-32 and 16-bit mixed precision for training ImageNet-64/128/256. All models are trained using the Adam optimizer with the following parameters: β1=0.9,β2=0.999 ,weight decay =0.0 ,and ϵ=1e−8 . All methods we trained (i.e.,FM-OT,FM-Diffusion,SM-Diffusion) using identical architectures, with the same parameters for the the same number of Epochs (see Table 3 for details). We use either a constant learning rate schedule or a polynomial decay schedule (see Table 3). The polynomial decay learning rate schedule includes a warm-up phase for a specified number of training steps. In the warm-up phase,the learning rate is linearly increased from 1e−8 to the peak learning rate (specified in Table 3). Once the peak learning rate is achieved, it linearly decays the learning rate down to 1e−8 until the final training step.

我们在表3中报告了使用的超参数。训练CIFAR10和ImageNet-32时使用全32位精度，训练ImageNet-64/128/256时使用16位混合精度。所有模型均使用Adam优化器训练，参数为：β1=0.9,β2=0.999，权重衰减为=0.0，以及ϵ=1e−8。我们训练的所有方法（即FM-OT、FM-Diffusion、SM-Diffusion）均采用相同架构，在相同的Epoch数下使用相同参数（详见表3）。学习率调度采用恒定学习率或多项式衰减（详见表3）。多项式衰减学习率调度包含预热阶段，预热阶段学习率从1e−8线性增加至峰值学习率（表3中指定），达到峰值后，学习率线性衰减至1e−8直至训练结束。
